Package: com.watchpair11
Name: WatchPair11
Version: 8.0-2
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: Pair Apple Watch watchOS 11.5 (Series 10+) with iPhone iOS 16.6. Single .deb works on both nathanlr (rootless) and roothide (Dopamine 2.x) jailbreaks. Includes optional native Apple Pay setup. Home-screen app for one-tap Apple Pay setup + rollback.
Maintainer: plokijuter
Author: plokijuter
Section: Tweaks
Depends: ellekit | mobilesubstrate (>= 0.9.5000), firmware (>= 15.0)
Replaces: com.watchpair11.tweak (<< 8.0), com.watchpair11.installer (<< 8.0)
Conflicts: com.watchpair11.tweak (<< 8.0), com.watchpair11.installer (<< 8.0)
Provides: com.watchpair11.tweak, com.watchpair11.installer
